00 | u64 (seconds) |\n| `AGENT_FARM_LOG_RETENTION_DAYS` | 30 | u32 |\n| `AGENT_FARM_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL` | 30 | u32 (seconds) |\n| `AGENT_FARM_GRACEFUL_SHUTDOWN_TIMEOUT` | 30 | u32 (seconds) |\n| `AGENT_FARM_LOG_LEVEL` | `info` | string |\n| `AGENT_FARM_OAUTH_TEST_ORIGIN` | none | optional URL override for OAuth testing |\n| `AGENT_FARM_GITHUB_API_BASE` | `https://api.github.com` | string |\n| `AGENT_FARM_GITLAB_API_BASE` | `https://gitlab.com` | string |\n| `AGENT_FARM_ANTHROPIC_API_BASE` | `https://api.anthropic.com` | string |\n| `AGENT_FARM_OPENAI_API_BASE` | `https://api.openai.com` | string |\n| `AGENT_FARM_ENCRYPTION_KEY_PREVIOUS` | none | optional for key rotation |\n| `AGENT_FARM_JWT_PUBLIC_KEY_PREVIOUS` | none | optional for key rotation |\n\n**AppConfig Struct Fields**:\n```rust\ndatabase_url: String\nbase_url: String\nencryption_keys: EncryptionKeys\njwt_keys: JwtKeys\nport: u16\ncors_origins: Vec<String>\nmax_concurrent_instances: u32\njob_dir_root: String\njob_cleanup_grace_period_secs: u64\nlog_retention_days: u32\nheartbeat_interval_secs: u32\ngraceful_shutdown_timeout_secs: u32\nlog_level: String\ngithub_client_id: Option<String>\ngithub_client_secret: Option<String>\ngitlab_client_id: Option<String>\ngitlab_client_secret: Option<String>\noauth_test_origin: Option<String>\ngithub_api_base_url: String\ngitlab_api_base_url: String\nanthropic_api_base_url: String\nopenai_api_base_url: String\nhost_wrapper_bin: String\nmcp_server_bin: String\nclaude_code_bin: Option<String>\ncursor_cli_bin: Option<String>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. AppState (`crates/api-server/src/state.rs`)\n\n**Shared State Struct**:\n```rust\npub struct AppState {\n    pub db: PgPool,                          // PostgreSQL connection pool\n    pub config: Arc<AppConfig>,              // Configuration\n    pub scheduler: Arc<dyn Scheduler>,       // Task scheduler\n    pub event_bus: EventBus,                 // Event broadcasting (pub/sub)\n    pub heartbeat_tracker: HeartbeatTracker, // I